Package com.hr.jtexgen.parser

Class Sentence

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hr.jtexgen.parser.Sentence
  • public class Sentence
extends java.lang.Object
    Sentence class represents a sentence. Sentence is defined as a sequence of words. Words are delimited by whitespace.

    Hasnain Raza
